'''三氯氧化钽'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为TaOCl<sub>3</sub>。它是[[钽|钽]]的[[卤氧化物|氯氧化物]]之一，其它已知的氯氧化钽还有TaO<sub>2</sub>Cl<ref name=Morozov>Morozov, A. I.; Karlova, E. V. Thermal stability of tantalum oxytrichloride and dioxychloride. ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1969. 14 (7): 1741-1745. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>和Ta<sub>3</sub>O<sub>7</sub>Cl<ref>Schaefer, Harald; Gerken, Rudolf; Zylka, Lothar. Oxidechlorides, -bromides, and -iodides of niobium and tantalum. ''Zeitschrift fuer Anorganische und Allgemeine Chemie'', 1986. 534. 209-215. ISSN: 0044-2313.</ref>。

==制备==
三氯氧化钽可由[[五氯化钽|五氯化钽]]和[[五氧化二钽|五氧化二钽]]在高温下反应得到。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Jenkins|first1=W.A.|last2=Cook|first2=C.M.|title=Tantalum oxychloride|journal=Journal of Inorganic and Nuclear Chemistry|volume=11|issue=2|year=1959|pages=163–164|issn=00221902|doi=10.1016/0022-1902(59)80062-2}}</ref><ref>Schafer, Harald; Sibbing, Engelbert. Chemistry of niobium and tantalum. XXV. The equilibrium Ta<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub> + 3TaCl<sub>5</sub> (gas) = 5TaOCl<sub>3</sub> (gas). ''Zeitschrift fuer Anorganische und Allgemeine Chemie'', 1960. 305. 341-348. ISSN: 0044-2313.</ref>
: Ta<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub> + 3 TaCl<sub>5</sub> {{eqm}} 5 TaOCl<sub>3</sub>
五氯化钽在氧气中加热（< 1000 °C），可以得到三氯氧化钽。<ref>Saeki, Yuzo; Matsushima, Tadahisa. Decomposition of niobium pentachloride and tantalum pentachloride with oxygen. ''Denko Kagaku'', 1964. 32 (9): 667-671.</ref>其它制法还有五氯化钽和[[一氧化二氯|一氧化二氯]]在[[四氯化碳|四氯化碳]]中的反应、五氯化钽和[[三氧化二锑|三氧化二锑]]在[[氯气|氯气]]流中的反应：<ref name=Kurt /><ref>Morozov, I. S.; Morozov, A. I. Reaction of tantalum oxychloride with alkali metal and ammonium chlorides and thermal stability of tetrachlorooxytantalates. ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1966. 11 (2): 335-341. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>
: TaCl<sub>5</sub> + Cl<sub>2</sub>O → TaOCl<sub>3</sub> + 2 Cl<sub>2</sub>
: 3 TaCl<sub>5</sub> + Sb<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> → 3 TaOCl<sub>3</sub> + 2 SbCl<sub>3</sub>

==性质==
三氯氧化钽在327 °C分解，生成TaCl<sub>5</sub>和TaO<sub>2</sub>Cl，后者氯氧化物在526 °C进一步分解，产生TaCl<sub>5</sub>和Ta<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub>。<ref name=Morozov />它和三丁基硼在80 °C开始反应，生成浅灰色的TaOB。<ref>Fedneva, E. M.; Buslaev, Yu. A.; Alpatova, V. I. Reactions of tantalum pentachloride and oxychloride with tri-n-butylboron. ''Izvestiya Akademii Nauk SSSR, Neorganicheskie Materialy'', 1970. 6 (5): 893-896. ISSN: 0002-337X.</ref>它可以在[[焦硫酸|焦硫酸]]中转化为硫酸氢盐：<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Bali|first1= A|last2=Malhotra|first2= KC|title=Behaviour of some niobium(V), tantalum(V) and molybdenum(VI) compounds in disulphuric acid|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_australian-journal-of-chemistry_1975-03_28_3/page/481|journal=Australian Journal of Chemistry|volume=28|issue=3|year=1975|pages=481|issn=0004-9425|doi=10.1071/CH9750481}}</ref>
: TaOCl<sub>3</sub> + 3 H<sub>2</sub>S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub> → TaO(HSO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub> + 3 HSO<sub>3</sub>Cl
: TaOCl<sub>3</sub> + 5 H<sub>2</sub>S<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub> → H[TaO(HSO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>4</sub>] + 3 HSO<sub>3</sub>Cl + H<sub>2</sub>S<sub>3</sub>O<sub>10</sub>
H[TaO(HSO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>4</sub>]与三氯氧化钽和[[氯磺酸|氯磺酸]]反应生成的H[Ta(SO<sub>3</sub>Cl)<sub>4</sub>]一样，是非电解质。<ref>Paul, R. C.; Kaur, Jaswinder; Konwer, D.; Puri, J. K. Solvolysis of various niobium(V), tantalum(V), molybdenum(V) and molybdenum(VI) compounds in chlorosulfuric acid. ''Indian Journal of Chemistry, Section A:  Inorganic, Physical, Theoretical & Analytical'', 1981. 20A (12): 1212-1214. ISSN: 0376-4710.</ref>

三氯氧化钽、五氯化钽、[[碲|碲]]和[[四氯化碲|四氯化碲]]在[[离子液体|离子液体]]{{link-es|1-丁基-3-甲基咪唑鎓氯化物|Cloruro de 1-butil-3-metilimidazolio|[BMIM]Cl}}中于190 °C反应，生成黑色的[Te<sub>8</sub>]<sub>2</sub>[Ta<sub>4</sub>O<sub>4</sub>Cl<sub>16</sub>]。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Freudenmann|first1=Dominic|last2=Feldmann|first2=Claus|title=[Te<sub>8</sub>]<sub>2</sub>[Ta<sub>4</sub>O<sub>4</sub>Cl<sub>16</sub>]: A Two-dimensional Tellurium Polycation obtained via Ionic Liquid-Based Synthesis|journal=Zeitschrift für anorganische und allgemeine Chemie|volume=637|issue=11|year=2011|pages=1481–1485|issn=00442313|doi=10.1002/zaac.201100143}}</ref>

三氯氧化钽可以和[[吡啶|吡啶]]（py）形成加合物TaOCl<sub>3</sub>·1.5py。<ref name=Kurt>Dehnicke, Kurt. Tantalum oxychloride. ''Naturwissenschaften'', 1965. 52 (3): 58. ISSN: 0028-1042.</ref>

